  "title": "Assistant Business Manager (Regional role/Fresh or no experience welcome)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Mon to Fri 8.30am to 5.30pm</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Salary $3500-$5500+$1000 car allowances+Petrol claim</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Location: Serangoon</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Industry: Marine/Oil &amp; Gas/Valve</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage existing accounts and identify new business opportunities to drive sales growth.</li>\n  <li>Plan customer visits and meetings, as well as provide technical support to customers</li>\n  <li>Coordinate and participate in industry trade shows to expand market reach</li>\n  <li>Develop and execute sales and marketing strategies to penetrate new markets</li>\n  <li>Conduct market research and analysis to identify trends and opportunities</li>\n  <li>Maintain and update sales progress reports</li>\n  <li>Meet sales revenue, profitability, and growth targets set by management</li>\n  <li>Ensure timely collection of payments and manage credit control</li>\n  <li>Work closely with supply chain and logistics teams to ensure smooth order fulfilment</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Minimum 2-3 years business development experiences</li>\n  <li>Minimum Diploma in any Engineering/ business management field</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Please submit your updated resume in MS format by using the <strong>APPLY NOW BUTTON.</strong></p>\n<p>Alternatively, you may also email your resume to us at <a href=\"mailto:emily.fong@atomrecruit.com\"><strong>emily.fong@atomrecruit.com</strong></a></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Emily Fong</strong></p>\n<p><strong>Senior Talent Specialist<br>\n</strong>Atomrecruit Pte. Ltd. | MOM EA License No.: 15C7443<br>\nEA Personnel Reg No.: R1768368</p>",
